The paper deals with image compression using deep learning techniques, specifically Convolutional Recurrent Neural Networks. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also involves training and optimization of the neural network, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper deals with data storage and retrieval, which falls under information theory (cs.IT) category.
